  "body": "I forked bsc and working hardhat on localhost.\r\nI have sometimes got this error.\r\nIt seems like it's working randomly. (even with same script)\r\nTwo cases (deploying and testing for the deployed contract) are the same.\r\nI noticed it happened if while going to write on contract. (i.e. to read on contract for test is working)\r\n\r\n```ProviderError: VM Exception while processing transaction: revert\r\n      at HttpProvider.request (node_modules\\hardhat\\src\\internal\\core\\providers\\http.ts:49:19)\r\n      at GanacheGasMultiplierProvider._getMultipliedGasEstimation (node_modules\\hardhat\\src\\internal\\core\\providers\\gas-providers.ts:72:59)\r\n      at GanacheGasMultiplierProvider.request (node_modules\\hardhat\\src\\internal\\core\\providers\\gas-providers.ts:309:19)\r\n      at runMicrotasks (<anonymous>)\r\n      at processTicksAndRejections (internal/process/task_queues.js:95:5)```\r\n\r\nAny solution? Thanks",
